comments: ['We have been using this app for years now. We appreciate Michael so much! He is consistently in touch with breeders, updating and adding fields and reports we need. He and his team care deeply in making life easier for breeders. Is this app perfect for everyone, perhaps not yet. No app we found is and believe in the effort and energy the team places into Breedera. Always improving. Thank you Breedera team!', 'This app is amazing!!!! I have used it since it started (previously known as Puppy Fat). I record vet visits, bottle feeding, growth charts, progesterone, health records, etc. I record all my dogs whether used for breeding or not. And you can save pictures of docs. I love that I can email reports to my vet, prospective owners, or myself or anyone else. Michael White, the developer, has always engaged us breeders for what WE needed and wanted to see. Give it a chance. You will LOVE it!!', "The app is actually decent for what it does, but all of the useful features are unavailable without the premium option. The main problem with this is that the app is too slow and has too many glitches for how much the premium costs. I wouldn't mind these issues if the app - or at least the most necessary features for breeders - was free, but I am not willing to pay for a broken system.", "Very disappointing! A notebook or spreadsheet could contain the same info that that's allowed to be listed here without payment...and for much, much cheaper! I just wanted something I can log into on my phone, without having to look up records on my desktop or in my filing cabinet. Something for on-the-go. Not a chance on earth I'd pay as much as they're asking for absolute basic record keeping. Too bad, this could have been a good app for myself and countless breeders I know.", "I want to like this app, however I can't log that I gave my dogs their regular preventatives on the free version. I feel that tracking preventatives should be a basic feature, not a paid one. I would have ended up paying for the app if I could get a better feel for the features before I pay or have to commit to a subscription. I get that you need to make your money, but logging preventatives should be free.", "Unfortunately not for me. Was really excited to have a look around this app. It could be brilliant and it might be in the future, but for now there's just not enough functionality for recording daily routine and exercise, breeding processes and nothing for recording whelping to justify the ¬£100 annual fee. May keep an eye on this app for future developments that make it a more comprehensive record keeping tool for the cost involved.", '$10 a month for basic logging? What the heck? Maybe $2.99 sounds reasonable, $10? No way.', "You can‚Äôt even do the one month trial without giving payment info so I deleted the app at that point. It would be better to offer limited functionality so you can give it a try and then buy the full app. I'm not a breeder with a lot of dogs. I have one dog that I have breed and just looking for something to help me track the litter.", 'You will find yourself not wanting to use the old ways. If the app does not have what you want just wait a little while it will be coming. I am going on my 3rd litter with this app and could not see it any other way. Even the vet was liking the growth charts the first time I went in for 6 week checkup. The sky is the limit on this app and the developer is awesome.', "Its very slow. You have to save info each time you enter ANYTHING. It doesn't generate any reports other than a weight graph. You can't print info on a specific puppy. You can't print anything. DEFINITELY NOT worth $1 much less $9.99 a month", "It keeps crashing when adding feedings so they don't save. Would like to be able to add puppy temperature monitoring and whelping box temp monitoring. Maybe vaccine and worming recording also? Maybe dame monitoring post partum also? Was hoping this app would capture and store more.", "Thank you for your improved platform. I'm giving 3 stars as I haven't has it long enough yet to properly assess but so far so good", 'Very helpful. Able to keep all of my contacts connected to the puppy. I can also see a growth chart of individual puppies and a whole litter chart. I highly recommend it.', 'Great idea but 99$ per year is a lot, we will have to stick with paper forms we found online for free. We dont breed dogs, for breeders who can afford it, itd be a great way to track everything! But we foster momma dogs pulled from euthanasia lists at shelter and whelp before altering them all and adopting out with a resuce and spent a lot of our own money raising the pups to 8wks and unfortunately 99$ isnt something we can afford yearly. If you can definitely go for it!', 'Wish I could give less. Page not loading', "Really! Horrible!!! Takes forever to load, then you have to create an account with verification code. THEN it tells you its 99.00 a year. That's just insane who would pay that!!!", 'Excellent app. Record keeping has all the options ,easy to use but the only way to print is screenshot.', 'Horrible waste of time not even worth takinh the space on your screen The owner will remove you from social media if you give an honest opinion. The app is slow Does not load Does not do what it should Think it was made on a barbie my first laptop And the best if it is after paying you 9.99 a month he wants you to find the flaws and tell him so they can fix you know like a beta version. This is possibly the worst app i have ever downloaded', "so far so good! it is my understanding that this app is new and a work in progress. so far it's amazing! I've been waiting for something like this! thank you for creating this Mike!", 'As a breeder I have found this app useful in managing my records of previous litters but also in planning my next breeding. The help and support that comes with the app cannot be underestimated answering my concerns getting advice was really welcome when I had an ill puppy from the associated social media group', "Going in BLIND. No one wants to pay for something they haven't even seen. I have no idea what the app even does. I want to give it a try but not with put any useful information. Wish I could write a good review...", "App won't even open anymore. Keep getting charged $10/month and no way to cancel.", "Waste of time. I need to sign up to find out I must pay! Make that information known from the beginning! So that I don't waste my time. Or atleast have a free option.", "Seems like a great app, but you can't use it without agreeing to pay $99/ year after the free 90 day trial.", 'looking forward to using this fully for my next litter. will make keeping all the records so much easier', 'Not free. It is a 1 month trial. 9.99 a month or 99 a year.', 'Very happy with all informations needed. Thanks for this great app!', 'I am loving this App', 'Too complicated. Next heat prediction is bogus. Puppy Planner is much better. Easy to read, understand and save. Their prediction base is not as shabby as PuppyFat.', "It's not free so how about you actually state that before you get my email address üôÑ Thanks for now asking me to remove my review üôÑ", "They don't tell you that this is a subscription service. Bunch of bull!!!!", 'Makes you pay a monthly fee to use', "Best App for breeder's", 'Waste of time. Useless app', '11pets is a better app', 'UGHHHHHH IT MAKES U SIGN UP I HATE THIS GAME', 'Makes you pay for it', 'Sucks', 'Worst ...']

title: Senior Match: Mature Dating
description:
‚ù§Google Play Editor's Choice‚ù§ - Trusted Mature Dating App for 50+ Silver Singles SeniorMatch is the #1 senior dating app for older women and mature men seeking like-minded singles of the same age. SeniorMatch.com aims to create an inclusive and friendly online dating app for senior people to find love and meet new friends. Started in 2003, SeniorMatch.com has 1,030,000+ senior singles over 50 and 36,600 success stories. We were mentioned in the movie Daddy's Home 2 and have been featured on Dating Advice, Dating News, Dating Scott, The Senior List and more.

Get Out There and Find Your Mature Match!

- Join the best online dating service for 50+ singles and baby boomers üíï Real Profiles - All profiles checked manually on a 24/7 basis to block bots and scammers üíï Senior-FRIENDLY - Easy to use app that empowers senior singles to match with people who share similar interests üíï Fun WINKS - Flirt with and meet new people near you on the community feed

Mature Dating: 50 is the new 20

As the #1 senior dating site, we know what it is like to be over 50. This exciting chapter of life is filled with freedom, wisdom and appreciation that only comes with time. Our online senior dating community focuses on the specific interests and desires of silver singles like you. We believe age doesn't matter when it comes to love. Give yourself another shot! You could be feeling butterflies by the weekend.

Ready to love again?

Thousands of seniors meet each day from the US, UK, Canada and Australia. We are also growing fast in Germany, Brazil and other parts of the world. Whether you are gay or straight, divorced or widowed, a single parent or childfree, SeniorMatch is a warm and safe place to find your special someone who is single now, just like you.

Not yet ready for love?

Senior Match is designed for 50+ dating, pen pals and to bring older singles together. Though as a senior dating app, it is also a meetup community where seniors feel free to discuss likes and dislikes, dating tips and relationship advice, over 50s fashion, and 50+ lifestyles after retirement. Even if you're not seeking someone special right now, as long as you're a silver single you can always enjoy this community. This is a safe place where you can meet new people and make some friends that are your own age.

PREMIUM SUBSCRIPTION

SeniorMatch, the mature dating app for silver singles, is free to download. To get the most of our app, we encourage users to subscribe to our optional premium subscriptions: ‚úìUnlimited communication with any senior you'd like ‚úìBe viewed and contacted 20+ times more than usual ‚úìEnjoy all these privileges across all platforms ‚úì24/7 customer service ... and much more. So what are you waiting for? It's time to focus on you and celebrate your golden years! Download the SeniorMatch app today.

comments: ["I spend 45 minutes, creating an account, uploaded picture and all, I get a phone call, after my phone call is over, nothing, the app wants me to start over, you would think that every time you hit continue tje app would save any and all information up to that point, nope, not this domb app, so unless you can ignore life 100% and complete this profile in its entirety don't even start, at least until you can lock yourself in a room by, secluded away from any distraction, otherwise forget it", "I've had such a good time using this app. It's super easy to use and I've recommended it to my friends after they've struggled with more complicated dating apps. I really don't understand all of the complaints. They are always available by email and are super responsive. Many people complained that they could not cancel their subscription but I have been both a paying and nonpaying member and haven't had an issue. I love this app and will continue sharing with friends!", "Absolute waste of money and time. You can't get anyone in your country, it keeps showing people in other countries, even though the setting is within your country. Many fake profiles, they don't respond immediately, they ask for more pictures but refuse to send theirs. The App is not user friendly. I have cancelled my subscription. Pictures are not matching their ages, response with very bad vocabularies. I wish I could get a refund", "As a senior, it isn't exactly easy to re-enter the dating pool, especially if you've been with a partner for a long time and that is no longer case. Senior Match makes it easy to date again, no matter what your age might be. It makes it easy to find people you have things in common with based on how you fill out your profile. It even takes the awkwardness out of trying to meet someone you are attracted to, which can be really hard if you haven't had to try for awhile. Thank you Senior Match!", 'Site has many issues with very few choices in my city, Mesa. I paid yesterday. Today they want me to pay again. No info for customer service. Scammers bigtimes. Very few are real peeps always attempting to get you to go to yahoo chat...I complained then it worked for a short while then it auto switches to men and not women, the distance I change to 50 miles instead of 500 then it requires me to pay again / reverts my subscription back to non paying. Not even close to what I paid for. Ripoff !!!', "It's difficult to read the words in the writing, and to answer the questions. The print is just too too small. Nancy", "keeps giving me people all over the country even when I set my local distance. Can't find how to update payment or cancel once I set it up. No one to contact for help. Found FAQs once, but can't find that again either. Big waste of money that I need to figure out how to cancel.", "A friend of mine met her husband using this site.. they saw each others pics, swiped, clicked, within 1 year, I was a bridesmaid. I want that for myself, too. I only just joined so far getting some interest.. but surprisingly and thankfully! It's super easy to navigate. At my age, i dont want complex... wish me luck, guys!", "SCAM BEWARE!! once you pay you never get anyone close to home. The email address they give you is not a real address. I can't communicate in any way what so ever! They take your money & don't deliver!", 'I find this site is clean and easy to use. I received many interesting people the way that I asked for. Does anyone want to meet some new friends or want to meet someone special? This is the place to be.', "I'm paying for this app but pof has given me more results for free .I will quit silver singles when expires", "Truly awful platform. 90% of contacts are catfish. I've been in contact with some people on the phone they say that messages don't get through. Either way. Don't waste your money on this application. Absolute garbage.", "I set this app up for my uncle, and we worked together on his awesome profile. Seems pretty straightforward, and he's liking how easy it is to navigate it and find women who share the same interests!", "WARNING!!! Don't install this App. I installed it and a few hours later they suspended my account. I really hadn't had any time to do anything on this site and now I can do nothing at all. When I contacted them by emial, they sent me a notice that I would have to send a picture of my drivers license or passport to prove I was real. It's a completed invassion of my private information. Now I can't even get to my notifications to turn them off. I keep getting notified though.", "WAY too expensive, and the app they purchased (from whomever) still has problems finding images on your phone. I can see the pics on my phone, but this app can't find the folder they're in. $35 for a single month is the smallest amount you can pay in order to actually use the app, and it's probably mostly lame people who will never meet you in person, or fake/abandoned profiles, like most other dating apps/sites.", 'App itself is good, but asks money for chat between not paid users.', 'I tried this last night. It has the same search engine as the Meet app (which only pulled up 2 registered females in my area). Using Senior Match, I went in and setup the filters (same interface as the Meet app, so it was easy to do). I specified women younger than me and within 30 miles. Not only was the app not able to display any registered women within 50 miles of me, but also every woman was much older than me. Maybe this site works better for people in large metropolitan areas. I guess I am stuck with the ghetto POF app.', "Less than no star!!!! I purchased the 1 month plan..... it sucks!!!, no connections at all..... I know that there is a more expensive package, maybe if you purchase that one the app might work for you. However I feel that if the app were legit it wouldn't matter which package you spent your hard earned money on...you would connect with someone at least one someone!!!. I sincerely would like to admonish any would be new subscribers to avoid this app!!!!!", "It doesn't let you complete the registration. When you take a video for verification it says check your Internet connection. Whereas every other app and device works perfectly! Me typing this message is proof to it. Also while filling up certain details it contradicts whats asked. There is repetition of information as well.", "None of the matches that I received were even in my area. Most of the people were either halfway across the country per their profile or overseas. Everything is text messaging constantly. When I did have a conversation with a couple of people they had a suspicious accent so I am immediately blocked them. It's just very overwhelming and I think most of the people on this site are scammers.", "Horrible! Mostly bots. Bots galore! You get hits but they're from 8 states away so you know it's a sham. In a few days, the account was deactivated. If anything is legit it's trailer park types. I'm glad I bought only one month. Canceled same day so I didn't get auto billed next month. Sham!", "This app is very easy to use, I don't like when people know I delete their messages so now I'm blocking more people, If not, I like its basics, Profile Info Go straight to the point and helpful in getting rid of people inside or out, Not just looking for a true love or sexual connection, but don't expect to find many people who really just want to chat with those like-minded people, I'm enjoying it,", "1. Seems like sophisticated scammers are on this site. watch out! 2. Difficult to renew membership once cancelled, this is really frustrating because there seems no way to do it, I've been trying, I've asked through the site and through Google Play for a call back, nothing so far!", 'I‚Äôve had some bad experience with dating apps in the past (including this one) but it seems that Senior Dating has really listened to our feedback and made significant improvements. I think the site is one of the best because they allow us to be ourselves and mingle with limited restrictions.', 'I use to like the app more when I just used the website. It was very handy and user-friendly. Now I need to get used to the app which is really difficult to me, coz you cant teach an old dog new tricks. Maybe its the matter of layout or just my personal preference, but I dont like the app as much as I love the website.', 'Senior Match is ok but I personally think that the only problem with is that people should be able to view their messages for free and not subscribe to just view the messages that were sent or to even reply back the messages should just be totally free. So I‚Äôm giving the app a 4th star.', "It's pricy. Maybe that'll keep people that don't want to spend money off the app and thats great.? Maybe it'll keep good selection away bc of more popular apps? I'd like to see a trail service.. maybe if there's enough responses I'd pay? Suggested to allow women free for a short while? Maybe more will join on a ladies trail? I dunno just saying", 'Overall, I like this senior dating app more than any other dating app because you have to pay for it and yes Better, well-researched questions. That means you can focus on finding more purposeful people who are actually trying to find someone, while other apps are just trying to hold you back to sell ads. Sow any cause meets the results.', 'Great app. Easy and great way to browse senior singles! Much better than when I used it a couple of years ago. Hopefully, they change the distance increments to smaller values at some point.', 'What a waste of time , most profiles no photos even when you state photos only, miles range does not work, put in a realistic range most people would and got profiles from all over the country and abroad that were just deleted.even had the wrong sex profiles come up, not a good experience dont bother.', 'This app is way not really allow you to look at many profiles and just has a poor design and not easy to use.', "No matches within 3 states of my location. Full of scammers. Scammers can be spoted if they don't verify their photo (which is very easy), or if their age range for a match is 40-99, or if they immediately ask for cell phone number or email.", "I thought I would get local singles instead these singles are states away. Out of the hundreds that I looked at only one is remotely even from my area. Unless you're willing to travel do not down load this app. It's junk I even messaged the company no response. Then I called there 855 number It's ALWAYS busy then I called their 416 number it just rings. No one ever answered the phone. I've called several times at different times of the day. And still no response. Don't pay for premium either", "Though not very often occasionally someone says hi. The biggest complaint I have is the search engine is rather useless. Regardless of the fact of what your parameters are set it's still insists on you looking at people that are hundreds of miles away or in different countries. That or they smoke or have other things not relevant to your interests. To make it even worse you swipe left to get rid of them & end up waiting for almost over a day to try again. 2022 & no response from the developers.", 'One thing I like it most is I can filter matches at any location, from America, Asian , Europe and Russia. I love it‚Äôs free to view unlimited profiles, but some messages are locked to view. Hope I can have more free messages.', "I can't complete your information. The submit is not highlight I have thr3e times. I will try again. Don't subscribe to this it is full of scammer. I find three. They had already deleted there account. If I could I would give the app a big fat zero 000. I hate been there a month. So, if you a guy don't use this app. Some of the women just want to send gift cards. So, be careful. And only chat on the app. Don't gave our phone to any if you do not trust them.", 'Complete waste of time and effort. The app is simply a way to get money from unsuspecting users and makes it impossible to connect with anyone unless you pay them outrageous monthly fees (assuming the anyones are genuine and actually live close to you). These dating apps seem to be just money-making devices since being bought out or created by profit-motivated commercial companies.', "This app is horrible, very few people in my area and I do live near a pretty decent sized city. Plus the only people contacting me were ones several states away, and most of them I determined were scamming, when they text you it's the exact same phrases word for word. Don't sign up for this app...", "I put on my profile, local, 100 miles or less and I kept getting people in Florida, New Jersey, etc Then, the one person that I matched with, turned out to be a fake. He literally quoted romance quotes from Google. Not kidding. Pathetic. Then, I get a random text on my phone. How did this guy even get my number??? The whole experience was disappointing. I had already paid for 1 month. Don't waste your time or money. I blocked the 2 guys, deleted my profile, and uninstalled the app.", "It's a nice concept app but the question is worth paying for? I've met a few women on this app and I like it. Sure someone will make a better free version soon. The quick searches could use someone revamping as well."]

title: Old Friends Dog Game
description:
Welcome to Old Friends Dog Game, where love never grows old! Create your own dog sanctuary in this heartwarming pet rescue simulator. Rescue adorable senior dogs and uncover their life story as you shower them with love. Decorate with cute doggy decor, bake scrumptious dog snacks, and experience the joy of helping cute senior dogs live out their golden years in the best way possible. 

Inspired by the real life pet residents at Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary, these cute dogs have heartwarming stories and personalities that you'll uncover as you rescue them and provide the care they need to live their best dog life!

Awarded Gold winner at the 2022 NYX Awards, a finalist for Pocket Gamer's Game of the Year, and a Webby honoree for Social Impact in Games, this cute dog simulator is a must-play!

Gameplay:

‚ù§Ô∏è Meet the town residents and rescue cute senior dogs. Help them live their best life by fulfilling their needs and ensuring their happiness. As you feed, pet, and play with your dogs, their love and loyalty grows.

üìò Choose how the story unfolds. In this dog simulator, you pick the path for each dog's story! Unlock multiple chapters for every cute doggy you rescue.

üíí Customize your dog sanctuary and make it a haven for your dogs. Decorate indoors and outdoors with cute doggy decor that will make your dogs feel right at home!

üßÅ Bake lip-smacking treats for your beloved dogs, ensuring they never go hungry.

üß£ Dress up your dogs in cute pet outfits! Each dog has adorable accessories that you can earn.

üêï Give your dog sanctuary the personal touch - feature a custom profile, a unique avatar, and a gallery of cute photos of each dog!

**********

Old Friends Dog Game is developed and published by Runaway.

This game is free to play but does contain some items available to purchase for real money. If you run into any issues while playing or you have any suggestions, please reach out to us at support@runaway.zendesk.com. OLD FRIENDS DOG SANCTUARY‚Ñ¢ is made by Runaway Play.

comments: ["Absolutely loving the game so far! I'm relieved it's not another match 3 or merge 2 games, and really is about taking care of old dogs and managing the sanctuary. I've seen the game's advert for a long time, I regret not playing it sooner. But better now than never I guess! Only thing is the game keeps crashing on me occasionally while loading a new scene (ex; getting a new dog, loading livestream, .etc) I love the game and I want to support the funding, I'd appreciate a smoother experience. :')", "I played the game a while ago and recently reinstalled it, but now it won't even let me past level one. Everytime I try to stream it just makes the screen go black, and nothing happens. I've tried everything to fix it, reinstalling again, restarting my phone, even went online to try and find an answer. Love the game, just wish I could get further with it.", "I absolutely love this game! It's adorable, and I haven't experienced any bugs (I have played for about a month now). Though, for the Dog Blog, there are limited color options, which, as someone with bright green hair, is a little saddening :( Aside from my dramatics about hair color, I recommend everyone give this game a try! It's so customized, and each dog has their own favorite treats and toys, which is so fun to memorize. I love this game!!", "This game is really amazing and I love the style so much! I really like the game because it's supporting a real life senior dog sanctuary too! But last 3 or 4 days I couldn't get in the game because i got a message about some kind of error and I tried everything to get rid of it but it hasn't been working so far. I got pretty good progress there so it's going to be sad if i lose it. I don't know if its a game error or its like that for someone too but I hope it gets fixed soon!", "Very Cute very relaxing it's really wholesome too! But, I've been having issues lately When I stream the screen becomes black and the music keeps playing and I can't go to the next level because my first time of streaming is glitching I've been having Issues with that so whatever you could do please Fix it....", "First things first, this is not a game you will play for an hour straight. More like a few minutes at a time. Gameplay is fun though. Little thing I mentioned pre-edit, So basically my progress reset, (It has been fixed now.) Devs should probably look into what caused that. Also I don't know if the message I sent to tell them it was fixed worked? All in all, great game, great devs. (What caused the game to reset though?)", "A awesome friendly game where you get to experience adventures and journey with these adorable dogs and the amazing artwork! I love this game. It's just heartwarming. And there is so much more potential to expand apon! The fact that it was based on real dogs and experiences is also amazing. You get to read snippets of real-world inspiration the further you progress.", "This is THE BEST chill/idle kind of game I've ever played. There's so much to do! You are always getting rewards constantly, even past the early game. There are only ads very rarely, when you want to increase your rewards. The dogs are so sweet and have personality that you uncover through their individual story lines. You'll fall in love. I had this game ages ago and left it like I always do with mobile games (I'm fickle lol) and this is the ONLY game I missed so much I had to come back again!", "This game is fun but I got stuck on the streaming stage Everytime I tried the screen would go black to the point I just left and rejoin the game and when I kept trying it took my stuff but never worked if u could see if it's a bug please update Soo it doesn't happen to other people", "it was almost an amazing game, except for the fact that it was lacking in furniture and decoration aspects. it's fun caring for the dogs, but i wish i could put more furnitures. there's so many furniture blueprints, but i cant craft becuz the materials for good furnitures are so hard to get. i wish we could buy materials from donations, or we could get from streams. idk. im quite unsatisfied witht the reward rn", "This make me cry so much. I love idle games. I love that this is based off an actual doggy sanctuary with the actual doggies and with pictures of the actual doggies attached. I'm sad and happy and my heart melt. Some lags and bugs are experienced and the game crashes too. But i just love the concept of this game. Good strategy to make ppl adopt senior dogs and cry cause they're gone too soon", "It's really great especially for dog lovers! I Love it a lot and especially that it's also a real sanctuary.. It really makes me wanna donate now :( but my parents do not allow me sadly... I hope some people will still donate :) definitely will recommend some friends to play this..!", "Old friends dog adventure is such a fun game where you care for older dogs and play the challenges! You get to choose what to say and there's even a dog blog! Definitely would recommend.", 'Sancuaty names could be more customizable(wanted to name mine after my old pup, Timber.) But otherwise, The game is amazing. The graphics are great. The dogs are adorable. And I love the hat for Mack.', 'Absolutely what I was looking for in a game, perfect with little to no ads and with very reasonable microtransactions! Would recommend', "Very cute! I would love if the game would emphasize the importance of identifying dog-friendly costumes that won't bother dogs vs coatumes that will make them uncomfortable all day, but overall its super fun üëç", "THIS GAME IS THE ACTUAL BEST! BAGEL IS SO CUTE MACK IS SO CUTE AND LEO IS SO CUTE,there's so many things to do!Decorate your sanctuary,collect new dogs,and it's all so much fun I love the theme and design of the game and how they're based on real life senior dogs!I wish I could meet them in real life!I was quite sad when I found out they only sold the merchandise in USD cuz I'm from the UK but seriously if I could I'd give this game a million bigillion stars out of a million biggilion stars!‚òÜ", "I am only on 3rd level, and I think it is really fun, cute, and great for a dog lover. I do find it a bit repetitive, but that will probably change over time. I olso do think Runaway's other games are really good too. If you delete their games, your progress will not be saved, though.", 'This game is so cute and entertaining! The dogs are adorable. Even the situations where almost nothing is going on it is really fun. Just baking food or cleaning the house just makes you feel happy and calm. I love this game and I really recommend this game for all dog lovers! ‚ù§Ô∏è', "It's such a cute game about dogs and don't love a dog for its age love it forever no matter what because old dogs are cute too and in the game you can unlock cute dogs like mack and bagel and Leo there so adorable doesn't matter how old a dog is love lasts for eternity I love Leo Babs and Captain Ron too runaway pls update maybe fix the bugs?
